form.congress: One Hundred Thirteenth Congress of the United States of America
form.enrolled-dateline: Begun and held at the City of Washington on Friday, the third day of January, two thousand and fourteen
form.official-title: Providing for a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 83.

section.text: That in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 83, the Clerk of the House of Representatives shall amend the long title so as to read: Making consolidated appropriations for the fiscal year ending September 30, 2015, and for other purposes..

attestation-group.role: Clerk of the House of Representatives.
